    Scaffold: VMOVAPS zmm_dest{kmask}{z}, [base_reg + offset]
    MachOpcode: SimdZmmLoad
    M1 fills per simd_backend_strict_emit_detail_part1.md §3 (EVEX load with disp8*64).
    """
